ars contract with her future employer and she is committed to finish.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\"><strong>Recommendation</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\">She shows willingness and determination to learn new things. She works as a domestic helper already and knows house works. I could see that she is hard working and dedicated to her work. I hope you give her a chance and view her profile and consider her then.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\"><strong>Video interview</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\">To view her personal video interview please click <a href=\"http://youtu.be/Bm-kDEzUDCQ\">https://youtu.be/Bm-kDEzUDCQ</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 100, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 22px;\">Eden Grace Maids and Employment Agency Pte Ltd</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: center;\">Address 61, Ubi Road 1, #03-36, Oxley Biz Hub, Singapore 408727<br />\r\nEmail <a href=\"mailto:edengrace_enquiry@yahoo.com.sg\">edengrace_enquiry@yahoo.com.sg</a><br />\r\nWEBSITE: <a href=\"http://www.edengracemaids.com/\">www.edengracemaids.com</a><br />\r\nOffice hours - Weekdays 9am to 6pm, Contact Person Chris Wong @ 91187703 or Alice Lee @ 92206000<br />\r\nAfter Office Hours- Weekends and Public Holiday, Contact Person - Alice Lee @ 92206000 or Susan Lee @ 83891511<br />\r\nOffice No: 66929011 /66929012 / 66929013</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: center;\">MOM LIC 13C6831</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: center;\