le=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\"><strong>Background</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\">She is 35 years old married, with 11 years old son. Stands 149 cm and her weight is 52 kg. The reason why she wants to work in Singapore is to support her family especially for the future of her son and her husband is agreeable that she apply for Singapore. Her mother in-law will be responsible for their son while she is in Singapore.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\"><strong>Personality</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\">She describes herself as a jolly person and teachable willing to learn things.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\"><strong>Experience</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\">She works in Lebanon for 1 year and 3 months, unfortunately because of the war between Lebanon and Syria she was not able to finish her contract and was sent back to Philippines.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\">The house is single story with 3 bedrooms. She wake up 5 o clock in the morning then she would start cleaning the hall way, computer room and dinning hall. After that she would wake the children (they are 10 & 8 years old) and sent them to school. When she return to the house she would continue to do house cleaning, doing Laundry and ironing as well.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\"><a href=\"http://www.edengracemaids.com/infant-care-live-in-nanny-singapore/\"><strong>Child care</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\">She can take care of new born baby and children as she is a mother herself and she also has experie