nd phone usage.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\"><strong>2 years contract</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\">She is aware that she will enter into 2 years contract with her future employer and she is committed to finish.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\"><strong>Recommendation</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\">She is suitable for childcare. She speaks well and she cooks and does household chores. She is willing to do eldercare. Being new to Singapore, she will need time to understand employer needs. With proper guidance she should be able to settle down and be a good helper.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\"><strong>Video interview</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\">To view her personal video interview please click <a href=\"https://youtu.be/XNz5CbblyjU\">https://youtu.be/XNz5CbblyjU</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal;\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 100, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 22px;\">Eden Grace Maids and Employment Agency Pte Ltd</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: center;\">Address 61, Ubi Road 1, #03-36, Oxley Biz Hub, Singapore 408727<br />\r\nEmail <a href=\"mailto:edengrace_enquiry@yahoo.com.sg\">edengrace_enquiry@yahoo.com.sg</a><br />\r\nWEBSITE: <a href=\"http://www.edengracemaids.com/\">www.edengracemaids.com</a><br />\r\nOffice hours - Weekdays 9am to 6pm, Contact Person Chris Wong @ 91187703 or Alice Lee 