xpresses herself that she loves pets and she is willing to learn and take care of pets.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Hand phone</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Susie is comfortable that her employer will keep her hand phone during working hours so that she can focus on her work.&nbsp; She will follow the employer&rsquo;s instruction regarding hand phone usage.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2 years contract</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Susie is aware that she will enter into 2 years contract with her future employer and she is committed to finish.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Recommendation</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Susie works in Singapore for quite some time; she learned new culture and has adjusted herself to different environment. She learned that Singapore has a high standard especially in cleaning and hygiene. As I could see, she had worked well in her last employer. She is more independent now and that was what she learned from her past experiences. I believe that would help her overcome new challenges in her future employer. I could see that she just needs a little time to settle down and she could work well in a new family. She is suitable helper to small family. Please view her profile and consider her then.</p>\r\n'),(262,'Lyza Mae Ferrer','1986-12-21','Buenavista Guimaras',157,60,11,'Philippines','Philippines','66929011','JAL293177','Christian',4,'','Ex-Singapore',1,'Separated',1,'9','48323.jpg','No','','No','','No','','','','1','','Singapore EA','',NULL,'','',53,'','2016-04-16 02:34:27','2016-04-16 06:34:27','N','70167.jpg','Available',0.00,'','','https://youtu.be/9jTEqZm302k',NULL,'<p><big><strong>Background</strong></big></p>\r\n\r\n<p><big>Lyza is 29 years of age, separated, and she has 1 child. She works in Singapore for 4 years and she is again applying to work as domestic helper because she needs to support her only child alone as she had been separated. While she will be away for 2 years, her parents will take care of her child.</big></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><big><strong>Personali