0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong>Experience</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">She works as helper in Malaysia for 2 months. Her responsibilities were to do house cleaning in a residential 2 storey house. She wakes up at 5:30 am to prepare herself to work. Then she will start to do work from sweeping to mopping and then wiping. She did not finish her contract for she needs to undergo an operation due to a lump on her breast. This time, she is better and good work well. In the Philippines, she experienced taking care of a crippled man for 2 years; she assisted him in taking shower, prepares his meals and does house cleaning. Aside from that, she is a mother who takes care of her son since birth.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong>Cooking</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; fon