 line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">Analiza is 30 years of age, married and she has 1 child age 8. She wants to work in Singapore as domestic helper to send money to her family. While away for 2 years, her husband will look after their child.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong>Personality</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">She describes herself as hardworking and flexible. She is someone who is a quiet type of person. She likes to cook and she loves children. Working in Singapore, she learned to communicate with her employer well.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong>Experience</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">Analiza works in Singapore for 1 year and 7 months. For her 1<sup>st</sup> employer, she works for 1 month; her responsibilities were taking care of children and also house work and cooking. Since this was her first time, she finds it hard to adjust to the grandma who also stays in the house who always nags at her. However, after she was transferred to 2nd employer, she worked a total of 1 year and 6 months. They lived in a condo with 2 bedrooms. There were 5 in the family. She did housework and cooking. She also did grocery with her employer. She was not able to finish her contract because her husband had an accident and she need to return back. In the Philippines, she took care of a 3 year old child for 1 year. She also did cooking and housework.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0